1-APR-88  SDP
    The UTIL directory is setup for command files and procedures
which are useful for more than one program or library.

For the first release it contains 4 opt files with the most commonly
used utility libraries:
UTIL.OPT             no debug, no DI3000
DEB_UTIL.OPT         debug version of UTIL.OPT
DI3000_UTIL.OPT      no debug for link file with DI3000
DEB_DI3000_UTIL.OPT  debug version of DI3000_UTIL.OPT
